            "description": "Primary activation of the gluteus maximus.",
            "instructions": "Support the upper back on a bench, plant feet flat on the floor with knees flexed at approximately 90 degrees. Extend the hips upward, fully contracting the glutes at the top. Avoid lumbar hyperextension by keeping the chin tucked and ribcage depressed.",
